dct_title_s: Vorderer Orient : Aussenhandel = Middle East : foreign trade
dct_description_sm: Dr. Ludwig Reichert Verlag. Companion text: Tuebinger Atlas des Vorderen Orients / Herausgegeben vom Sonderforschungsbereich 19 der Universitat Tubinger. Wiesbaden : Dr. Ludwig Reichert Verlag, 1977- Issued in fascicles. Supplements and other related publications (Arbeitsheft and Beiheft). ISBN: 1882267402. North Decimal Degree 42.028611. South Decimal Degree 12.557778. East Decimal Degree 71.121944. West Decimal Degree 38.013611. Map is: fascicle TAVO A X 20 of "Tuebinger Atlas des Vorderen Orients: TAVO." Five maps on one sheet: 1.1. Vorderer Orient. Handelspartner = Middle East. Trade partners. 1.2: Vorderer Orient. Warengruppen = Middle East. Merchandise groups. 2.1 Turkei. Importe nach Warengruppen 1982 = Turkey. Imports according to merchandise groups 1982 (1:8,000,000). 2.2 Turkei. Zollstellen = Turkey. Custom points (1:8,000,000). 2.3 Turkei. Exporte nach Warengruppen 1982 = Turkey. Exports according to merchandise groups 1982 (1:8,000,000). Source: "MEED (verschiedene Jahrgaenge) MEED Special Reports ( Auswahl: UN Statistical Yearbook 1981, New York 1983, Yearbook of International Trade Stat. 1982, New York 1984"; "Foreign trade statistics 1982, State Institute of Statistics, Publ. 1063, Ankara 1984." ISBN: 3882262402.
dct_publisher_sm: Wiesbaden : Herausgegeben vom Sonderforschungsbereich 19 "Tuebinger Atlas des Vorderen Orients", 1986.
